A title by contract is avoided by indicating a limitation in respect of time or place or

condition or alternative. In general the grounds of the original nullity of a disposition are

either: (a) Want of the conditions necessary to its validity, whether from absence of the personal qualities required in the disposer, or 'from

(b) Or prohibition of the disposition by positive law.
